data.description: Welcome to your dream home in Plainfield, Indiana! This stunning 3-bedroom, 2 1/2-bathroom residence with a loft is the epitome of comfort and style. Step onto brand-new luxury vinyl plank (LVP) flooring that flows seamlessly throughout the main level, creating a warm and inviting atmosphere. The open-concept living space is perfect for both entertaining and everyday living. Ascend the stairs to discover the master suite, a tranquil retreat featuring not one but two walk-in closets-ensuring you have all the space you need for your wardrobe. The additional two bedrooms are generously sized and share a well-appointed full bathroom. The loft area provides a flexible space that can be customized to suit your needs-a home office, play area, or cozy reading nook. This home comes with an unfinished basement that is already plumbed, presenting an excellent opportunity for customization and expansion. Imagine creating a media room, fitness center, or additional living space tailored to your unique preferences.    Conveniently located in Plainfield, you'll enjoy easy access to local amenities, parks, and schools. Don't miss the chance to make this house your home. Schedule a showing today!
